    "en": {
      "title": "Fuel prices drop - here's the new price list",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Sri Lanka Petroleum Corporation has announced that the price of fuel has been reduced in the country with effect from 10.00 pm today (17).",
        "In that way, the Sri Lanka Petroleum Corporation has reduced petrol by 20 rupees and diesel by 20 rupees. It is also noteworthy that Super Diesel has been reduced by 10 rupees and Octane 95 petrol by 10 rupees.",
        "The Petroleum Corporation has also informed that fuel will be distributed from July 21 as per the new \"Fuel Pass\" system."
      ],
